Hi Survivors, get ready for the descent! Even if you know when you're going in, you won't know when you're going out... if you ever do!

This mod generates cave networks all around the map, including dedicated underground and entrance prefabs.

It is under active developement and relies on the community contributions to evolve accross the time and to show his full potential.

Find more details, and see how it was coded on the [url=https://github.com/VisualDev-FR/7D2D-Procedural-Caves]github repo[/url][url=https://github.com/VisualDev-FR/7D2D-efficient-base-repair] [/url]of the project

