[b][size=3]Included features[/size][/b]

[list]
[*][size=2]Procedural cave system generation (need to create a new world from rwg)[/size]
[*][size=2]Cave zombies - Watch out when exploring caves, you'll not be alone ![/size]
[*][size=2]Cave bloodmoon - Avoid spending your bloodmoon in caves, you'll have been warned ![/size]
[*][size=2]Cave lighting - Caves are dark, flashlights will slowly decay overtime and will need to alimented with AA batteries, and a new light source have been introduced : the road flares, throw them away in caves to light-in your path ![/size]
[*][size=2]Prefab editor plugin: a command-line to accessible from the prefab editor, to make easier the cave prefab design process[/size]
[*][size=2]Cave loot - terrain blocks and loot containers found in caves will offer new collectible items. Use them to craft an entire set and sell them to trader ![/size]
[/list]
