[b][size=3]How to Install Manually[/size][/b]

[list=1]
[*]Ensure to have the mod TFP_Harmony installed in your mods folder
[*]Download the [[b]zip file[/b]] of the mod.
[*]Extract the entire content of the zip file to `C:\...\Steam\steamapps\common\7 Days To Die\Mods\`.
[*]Check that these 4 folders have been installed: [b]TheDescent[/b], [b]cave-assets[/b], [b]cave-lights[/b] and [b]cave-prefabs[/b]
[/list]
[b][size=3]NOTES[/size]
[/b][list]
[*][b][size=3]This mod is not EAC compatible[/size][/b]
[*][b][size=3]The Vanilla mod TFP_HARMONY is required to make this mod working[/size][/b]
[*][b][size=3]Cave maps cannot be generated from servers due to potential high resources consumption. It mean that you'll have to generate your world in local then to import it on your server[/size][/b]
[*][b][size=3]Generation for worlds over 10k might work but is not guaranteed and might require lot of RAM / CPU[/size][/b]
[/list]

